{"tid":858649,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自殺後會唔會好似瞓覺咁舒服？","createTime":"2018-10-12T03:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T03:25:58.000Z","uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"038c7506be5a710b58bc1241173cfc886107709c","tid":858649,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:20:19.000Z","msg":"有時有煩惱唔想諗野就會瞓覺，因為大腦唔會再諗其他野，一起身個腦就煩其他野。<br />\n我知道自殺係會有一小段時間痛苦，但之後就應該瞓覺咁舒服，就好似古人稱早登極樂。<br />\n日日煩將來條路點行，後悔自己讀個科blablabla，有自殺的念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad20fd7876be04454aa7dea9cab9634a4242252","tid":858649,"uid":59410,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。<br />\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline</a>"},{"pid":"369e5de1ce109bf2ad6d4cdb23fc5b36af347658","tid":858649,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bad20fd7876be04454aa7dea9cab9634a4242252","tid":858649,"uid":59410,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。<br />\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"學術討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c37496659ee1bb5ee27064321b387d0edcb04f5","tid":858649,"uid":59410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"有自殺的念頭仲學術討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34501014201664c7dabaeb1b1e50cec126988617","tid":858649,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:23:22.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常困苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，到我們的網站[url] <a href=\"http://help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhelp4suicide.com.hk&d=z5r78ieZp71fnBT0IHEi3dWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=f7ea2af2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">help4suicide.com.hk</a> [/url]。那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『真心話室』（星期一至五，下午８時至１２時）即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"9e590c65b705454795a3135a613bf6f3e78c503b","tid":858649,"uid":59440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"369e5de1ce109bf2ad6d4cdb23fc5b36af347658","tid":858649,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bad20fd7876be04454aa7dea9cab9634a4242252","tid":858649,"uid":59410,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。<br />\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"學術討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"大哂？之前單屯門三屍案咪又係話學術討論"},{"pid":"5b8da9dd39dbca7671ac29414922579199f1ab50","tid":858649,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5c37496659ee1bb5ee27064321b387d0edcb04f5","tid":858649,"uid":59410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"有自殺的念頭仲學術討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm